    <h2 class="date-header">February 26, 2019</h2>

	<div class="entry-category-music entry-author-glenn_kenny entry-type-post entry" id="entry-6a00e5523026f58834022ad39f2ee5200c">
       <div class="entry-inner">
					<h3 class="entry-header"><a href="https://somecamerunning.typepad.com/some_came_running/2019/02/notable-recordings-of-2018.html">Notable recordings of 2018</a></h3>
		



		<div class="entry-content">

